<hometopic>Properties Help

Use the Properties dialog box to change file and folder permissions, to add and modify an Access Control List (ACL) associated with a file or folder, and to view information pertaining to a file or folder. 

The Properties dialog box Category radio buttons present two options:
Permissions and Information. The Permissions dialog box is the default view 
for the Properties dialog box. Select Information to view the Information
dialog box. 


